-------------------------------
* What is Renesas Condor ?
-------------------------------

	elinux
	https://elinux.org/R-Car/Boards/Condor

	RTP0RC77980SEBS012SA01
	https://www.renesas.com/us/en/products/automotive-products/automotive-system-chips-socs/rtp0rc77980sebs012sa01-adas-automated-driving-solution-r-car-v3h-reference-board-condor-i

-------------------------------
* Condor vs Condor-I
-------------------------------

	V3H  Condor	= r8a77980  = RTP0RC77980SEB0010S
	V3H2 Condor-I	= r8a77980A = RTP0RC77980SEB0012SA01

	This script is tested on "V3H2 r8a77980A Condor-I board"

-------------------------------
* How to get ROM ?
-------------------------------

	Please Contact to [Renesas Sales team] or
	[Renesas appointed store Sales team]

-------------------------------
* Where is ROM / TeraTerm macro ?
-------------------------------

** ROM
	You need to get "sdk1" package for ROM

		rcar-xos_platform-sdk1_v3.37.0_release.tar.gz

	You can find ROM at

		rcar-xos/${VERSION}/os/bootloader/${BOARD}

** TeraTerm macro

	You need to get "StartupGuide" package for TeraTerm macro

		R-CarV4H_V4M_V3H_V3M_SDK_StartupGuide_${VERSION}.zip

	You can find TeraTerm macro at

		R-CarV4H_V4M_V3H_V3M_SDK_StartupGuide_${VERSION}/teratermmacro/

